---
import { ArrowRight, Layers } from 'lucide-astro';
import { withBase } from '../../utils/paths';

const contactoHref = withBase('contacto/');
const solucionesHref = withBase('soluciones/');
---
<section class="relative py-32 pb-24 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800">
  <img
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?w=1400&h=600&fit=crop&q=80"
    alt=""
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-15 mix-blend-luminosity"
    loading="eager"
    aria-hidden="true"
  />

  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10"
    style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,212,170,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,212,170,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;"
    aria-hidden="true"
  />

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 text-accent
               px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6
               animate-fade-in opacity-0"
        data-animate
      >
        <Layers size={14} stroke-width={2} />
        Metodología TAC ADVISORS
      </div>

      <h1
        class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-6
               animate-fade-in opacity-0"
        style="animation-delay: 100ms;"
        data-animate
      >
        Contabilidad, estrategia financiera e inteligencia de datos para empresas que quieren
        <span class="text-accent">crecer con orden</span>
      </h1>

      <p
        class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto
               animate-fade-in opacity-0"
        style="animation-delay: 200ms;"
        data-animate
      >
        Ayudamos a empresas a tomar mejores decisiones financieras mediante una combinación de
        contabilidad, planeación tributaria, análisis de datos y criterios estratégicos apoyados
        por tecnología e inteligencia artificial.
      </p>

      <p
        class="text-base text-accent/90 font-semibold mb-10
               animate-fade-in opacity-0"
        style="animation-delay: 250ms;"
        data-animate
      >
        Convertimos información dispersa en claridad, control y decisiones más acertadas.
      </p>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4
               animate-fade-in opacity-0"
        style="animation-delay: 300ms;"
        data-animate
      >
        <a
          href={contactoHref}
          data-booking
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2
                 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-accent-hover
                 text-white font-semibold text-base
                 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg
                 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out
                 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[0_8px_16px_rgba(0,212,170,0.3)]"
        >
          Agendar consulta gratuita
          <ArrowRight size={18} stroke-width={2} />
        </a>
        <a
          href={solucionesHref}
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2
                 border border-white/20 text-white font-semibold text-base
                 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg
                 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out
                 hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/40"
        >
          Conocer nuestros servicios
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
